So for the phone-shop,

00:01:11.580 --> 00:01:16.635
let's add the URL extension of phone-shop.

00:01:16.635 --> 00:01:20.650
The site title also is Phone Shop,

00:01:21.550 --> 00:01:24.245
the language of your choice,

00:01:24.245 --> 00:01:27.030
and then add in an e-mail.

00:01:30.370 --> 00:01:34.265
So you may have just noticed there when typing the e-mail,

00:01:34.265 --> 00:01:38.585
the WordPress has recognized this is a existing user,

00:01:38.585 --> 00:01:42.735
or a existing administrator, and therefore,

00:01:42.735 --> 00:01:47.475
the phone-shop we've added to the admin panel for this user.

00:01:47.475 --> 00:01:49.665
Just like it says blow,

00:01:49.665 --> 00:01:54.079
