00:01:54.079 --> 00:02:00.140
WordPress will automatically create a new user for this admin e-mail address.

00:02:00.140 --> 00:02:02.970
Click on "Add Site".

00:02:06.650 --> 00:02:10.830
Now if we go back over to My Sites at the top.

00:02:10.830 --> 00:02:13.209
